| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5708 — Recovery Inhibition (apt73)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0f3536e5-2a1a-53db-b3bd-afaeb5ad9d94"
